subject: Rajasthan History
topic: Rajasthan's Capital and Other Famous Cities
question_en: Which city is the capital of Rajasthan and which are the other famous cities?
question_hi: राजस्थान की राजधानी है। राजस्थान में अन्य पसंदीदा शहरे।
explanation_en:
Jaipur is the capital of Rajasthan and Udaipur, Jodhpur, and Bikaner are other famous cities in Rajasthan.
